```plantuml
@startuml philipplackner_IvyWallet-PL_Version
actor User

participant "HomeViewModel" as HomeVM
participant "Transaction Management" as TransMgmt
participant "Account Management" as AccMgmt
participant "Category Management" as CatMgmt
participant "Data Sync Module" as DataSync
participant "Backup/Restore Module" as BackupRestore
participant "Exchange Rates Module" as ExRates
participant "Formula Module" as FormulaMod
participant "UI Design System" as UIDesign
participant "File System" as FileSys
participant "Notifications" as Notifications

User -> HomeVM: Interact with Home Screen
HomeVM -> TransMgmt: Manage Transactions
HomeVM -> AccMgmt: Manage Accounts
HomeVM -> CatMgmt: Manage Categories

HomeVM -> DataSync: Synchronize Data
DataSync -> BackupRestore: Backup/Restore Data

HomeVM -> ExRates: Fetch Exchange Rates
HomeVM -> FormulaMod: Execute Formulas

HomeVM -> UIDesign: Utilize Design System
User -> FileSys: Perform File Operations
User -> Notifications: Manage App Notifications

